              <span id="reviewTextContainer82429089" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16238345268121599951">Nice followup read for people who enjoyed The God Delusion by Richard Dawkins or similar works. Describing religion as a virus with the main goal being to protect and propogate the virus really encouraged deeper thought for me about my thoughts on religion.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

